def: A series of prayers (see Note below) arranged to be recited inorder, on beads; also, a string of beads by which the prayers arecounted.His idolized book, and the whole rosary of his prayers. Milton.
In a disinterested manner; without bias or prejudice.
Any fact or truth which is decisively attested or intuitivelyknown as a psychological or philosophical datum; as, the deliveranceof consciousness.
Of or pertaining to polycrotism; manifesting polycrotism; as, apolycrotic pulse; a polycrotic pulse curve.
Containing mammalian remains; -- said of certain strata.
A certain rate per cent; the allowance, duty, rate of interest,discount, or commission, on a hundred.
In a dim or obscure manner; not brightly or clearly; withimperfect sight.
Birds which are able to run about and obtain their own food assoon as hatched.
Of or pertaining to chemical action of light, or produced byit; as, the photochemical changes of the visual purple of the retina.
